{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 21:20:11.810706", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission completed.\n\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty devices: leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1\n- Root cause: bmv2_switch_down\n\nRationale summary:\nAll OVS-based switches (leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1) have their switching services inactive (dead). With fail_mode=secure and a configured controller target, OVS drops all traffic without an active controller session, resulting in complete L2 forwarding failure and ARP flooding suppression across the fabric.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2100, "output_tokens": 108, "total_tokens": 2208, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 0}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
